ities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Liema Pantsi's victory was clouded as fans of the 'Big Brother Mzansi' show expressed that Smash Afrika was unprofessional towards her.\", \"from\": 7674, \"to\": 7809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7725, \"end\": 7736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Brother_(franchise)\", \"score\": 0.7225482040436585, \"rank\": 0.24191882124760444, \"text\": \"Big Brother\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Brother_(franchise)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Brother_(franchise)\"}, {\"begin\": 7771, \"end\": 7777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maghreb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1928663853425633e-24, \"text\": \"Afrika\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maghreb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maghreb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A dominant weekend for the SA teams in the URC has made a big impact on the latest log standings as the playoffs edge closer.\", \"from\": 7811, \"to\": 7936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7838, \"end\": 7840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.8600787138758e-20, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 7854, \"end\": 7857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\", \"score\": 0.9999874607860327, \"rank\": 1.2539026767426544e-05, \"text\": \"URC\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q10962\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheSouthAfrican.com is all about South Africa and the stories that affect South Africans, wherever they are in the world.\", \"from\": 7940, \"to\": 8061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7973, \"end\": 7985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\",